result.name: Zenpachi

reviews.text: Good service. Good spacious private environment. Good food.
Good japanese restaurant for sabu sabu

Good address for quality ingredients and good choice. The restaurant has lunch menus below 200HKD, while for dinner the prices go naturally up. Reservation is advisable, especially in peak hours or if you want to have a nice booth with Kowloon Park view. 
The environment is pleasant and the service swift. You can't miss the building (just look for the Apple store in Canton Road, while keep in mind that you have to take one elevator for the second Lobby on the 5th floor then another one to go up to the restaurant.
Excellent quality lunch sets for under $200
Got a cockroach in the tea, and the manager didn’t want to do anything but arrogantly asked us to call police if we wanted. Please don’t come here!
